      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled distinction. This specimen remains in exemplary showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation that challenges the passage of time. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care synonymous with a private collection. Mechanically sound and aesthetically beyond reproach, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising quality and investment-grade excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
